# systemd-sysusers(8) configuration for http-smtp-rele.
#
# Creates a dedicated system user and group if DynamicUser is not used
# (e.g. when running on older systemd versions).
#
# Installation:
#   install -m 644 http-smtp-rele.sysusers \
#       /etc/sysusers.d/http-smtp-rele.conf
#   systemd-sysusers

# Type  Name               ID   GECOS                        Home          Shell
u       http-smtp-rele     -    "http-smtp-rele daemon"      /var/lib/http-smtp-rele  -
